Reasoning: The paper discusses the interplay between different participants in the internet advertising ecosystem and the research issues related to it. Information Retrieval (cs.IR) is a key aspect of internet advertising as it involves matching ads to user queries. Digital Libraries (cs.DL) is also relevant as it involves managing and organizing large amounts of advertising data. Social and Information Networks (cs.SI) is relevant as it involves understanding user behavior and preferences. Multimedia (cs.MM) is relevant as it involves the use of images and videos in advertising. Finally, Sociology (cs.SOC) is relevant as it involves understanding the impact of internet advertising on society.
